506
00:32:26,978 --> 00:32:28,207
Give them to me.

507
00:32:30,449 --> 00:32:31,974
I'm waiting patiently.

508
00:32:33,785 --> 00:32:35,083
I'm not getting anything.

509
00:32:36,288 --> 00:32:37,312
Show me.

510
00:32:45,464 --> 00:32:46,488
Check the leads?

511
00:32:53,638 --> 00:32:54,833
Still nothing.

512
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,636
Maybe there'll be
some neuroplasticity.

513
00:32:58,143 --> 00:33:00,806
Her brain, it
could rewire itself.

514
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,739
No.

515
00:33:05,083 --> 00:33:08,645
Zero brain activity. I don't
know why, but she's gone.

516
00:33:27,472 --> 00:33:28,496
What?

517
00:33:28,607 --> 00:33:30,508
Your neurosurgery
patient that died tonight.

518
00:33:30,609 --> 00:33:32,009
There's something
you should know.

519
00:33:32,377 --> 00:33:33,436
What?

520
