Okay, Marco, I want you
to try to move your toes.

521
00:33:55,033 --> 00:33:56,057
I can't.

522
00:33:56,535 --> 00:33:58,299
- Is he okay?
- We're not sure if the bone...

523
00:33:58,370 --> 00:33:59,736
But he's not gonna die.

524
00:33:59,838 --> 00:34:01,898
He's not gonna get an
infection, his body's not...

525
00:34:02,007 --> 00:34:03,684
We're monitoring
him very closely.

526
00:34:03,708 --> 00:34:05,628
- The biggest threat is behind him...
- He moved.

527
00:34:06,378 --> 00:34:07,402
He moved.

528
00:34:14,386 --> 00:34:15,547
It worked.

529
00:34:17,389 --> 00:34:19,000
You have a long recovery ahead,

530
00:34:19,024 --> 00:34:20,185
months of physical therapy.

531
00:34:20,258 --> 00:34:22,159
But for now, all you
have to do is rest.

532
00:34:22,227 --> 00:34:23,251
Thank you.

533
00:34:23,895 --> 00:34:25,523
Thank you for saving my life,

534
00:34:26,398 --> 00:34:27,422
for saving my leg.

535
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:30,620
- Thank you.
- You're welcome, sir.

536
00:34:35,574 --> 00:34:37,338
Are you ready to
finish what we started?

537
00:34:39,778 --> 00:34:40,837
Get well first.

538
00:34:42,581 --> 00:34:44,413
There's plenty of
time for a wedding.

539
00:34:53,091 --> 00:34:55,788
- Thank you. Thank you.
- You're welcome, sir.

540
00:35:03,768 --> 00:35:06,932
You look good.
Tough, like Aquaman.

541
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:13,110
I look like sushi.

542
00:35:13,411 --> 00:35:14,777
Everybody loves sushi.

543
00:35:16,548 --> 00:35:17,880
It's only for six months.

544
00:35:17,949 --> 00:35:20,384
Your new skin should have
completely grown in by then.

545
00:35:20,452 --> 00:35:21,818
You should have minor scarring.

546
00:35:23,221 --> 00:35:24,314
Thank you.

547
00:35:26,891 --> 00:35:28,325
I misjudged you.

548
00:35:30,495 --> 00:35:31,724
You judged me just right.

549
00:35:44,409 --> 00:35:45,638
She's still sleeping?

550
00:35:46,945 --> 00:35:48,743
- You haven't told her yet?
- No.

551
00:35:50,482 --> 00:35:51,916
Can I have a moment, please?

552
00:35:52,951 --> 00:35:54,146
Of course.

553
00:36:01,292 --> 00:36:02,920
How soon after you found Jenna

554
00:36:02,994 --> 00:36:05,657
